---
/**
 * Skip to Content Component
 *
 * Accessibility feature that allows keyboard users to bypass navigation
 * and jump directly to main content. Link is visually hidden until focused.
 *
 * Features:
 * - Visually hidden by default (off-screen positioning)
 * - Becomes visible on keyboard focus (:focus, :focus-visible)
 * - High z-index to ensure visibility above all content
 * - Smooth scroll behavior (respects prefers-reduced-motion)
 * - Semantic HTML with descriptive text
 *
 * WCAG 2.1 Compliance:
 * - Success Criterion 2.4.1 (Bypass Blocks) - Level A
 * - Provides mechanism to skip repeated navigation blocks
 *
 * @component
 * @example
 * <SkipToContent />
 *
 * Usage:
 * Place at the very top of <body>, before any other content.
 * Requires corresponding id="main-content" on target element.
 */
import styles from './skip-to-content.module.css';
---

<a href='#main-content' class={styles.skip}> Skip to main content </a>
